Allan Cuthbertson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Allan_Cuthbertson 0 Allan Darling Cuthbertson (7 April 1920 – 8 February 1988) was a naturalised Anglo-Australian actor. He was best known for playing stern-faced military officers in British films of the 1950s and 1960s.
